@startuml seq_23_create_community
title Sequence Diagram: UC-23 Create Community

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Community Controller" as Controller
participant "Community Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Community Repo" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Fill community details & attach media
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/communities (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: Create Community
Service -> Repo: Check community name availability
Repo --> Service: Name is available

alt Media (avatar/banner) attached
    Service -> Cloudinary: Upload media stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> Repo: Insert new Community record
Repo --> Service: Community created (ID)

Service -> Repo: Add creator as Community Admin/Owner
Repo --> Service: Role assigned

Service --> Controller: Created Community Data
Controller --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend --> User: Redirect to new community page
@enduml